{"tid":1213702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察同有親戚朋友係警察既入黎","createTime":"2019-06-13T02:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T02:50:46.000Z","uid":97162,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1f17702abb670f76fa1544cb5e6791e02c532c3a","tid":1213702,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:26:41.000Z","msg":"留左幾個post都冇人理決定自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地今日係政治工具，幫政府過逃犯條例<br />\n只要條例一過香港慢慢赤化，公安權力大過警察<br />\n只要有乜事，你地就係棄子，第一個交你地上去砌生豬肉<br />\n市民連同情都唔會有，係自己身邊行過個個鄙視，變過街老鼠<br />\n而且同大陸接軌外資撤走港紙貶值，你地自豪既起薪一齊貶<br />\n你地都會有仔女，你今日做既係佢地受<br />\n香港收皮，你地會係最霉個堆<br />\n<br />\n唔期待前線個堆會睇得明<br />\n但希望仲有少量後排有良心既會明<br />\n仲有考緊同準備考既"},{"pid":"f6bd1a3d09fa538add39716acadab9f212ca4b6b","tid":1213702,"uid":97162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:27:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c2dce7900ca1ed8b35dc1a11c71bf6e8580d480","tid":1213702,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:28:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1d7ebed2f56a84693f523a2e66074590ff8ed55","tid":1213702,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8afa3ea73c65c38ed56b149d18633b570d93bda0","tid":1213702,"uid":25391,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:28:40.000Z","msg":"經過琴日已經冇得返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0678b140b6d98d64e79b7e5e8d4044c68179bdd","tid":1213702,"uid":97162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56a0912f54186fcff1a4ea03220f1a2e37dce646","tid":1213702,"uid":183781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"次次有咩都話和平理性<br />\n睇下仲有幾多次和平理性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩唔好俾機會狗察老解<br />\n講到好似得香港有軍/警咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩完一晚<br />\n今日二讀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抗爭/革命 有邊次唔流血"},{"pid":"74ae44c21a11c37